name: Conte Sans (iOS13)
author: Evelyn (ev_ynw)
description:
100% size. Install 'Conte Sans_85% (iOS13)' for smaller character size.

Only compatible on iOS13. iOS10-12 users please install the package marked “iOS10-12”.

Installed to: /Library/Themes/[fontname].theme/
